We begin by noting the two facts that mention the individuals in question:
 • “Jeffrey is Andrea’s descendant” (so Andrea is an ancestor of Jeffrey).
 • “Alan is Keith’s ancestor” (so Keith is a descendant of Alan).

Aside from these, nowhere in the provided relationships is any link given that connects Andrea’s branch of the family to Keith’s branch. There is no information to indicate that Andrea is anywhere above, below, or even related (by sharing an ancestor or descendant) with Keith.

Thus none of the listed relationships (Andrea being Keith’s descendant, sharing a common ancestor, sharing a common descendant, or Andrea being Keith’s ancestor) can be confirmed based on the given data.
